description: Germany says Alexei Navalny was attacked with a type of nerve agent used against an ex-spy in the UK.
title: Alexei Navalny: Russia opposition leader poisoned with Novichok - Germany
title_page: Alexei Navalny: Russia opposition leader poisoned with Novichok - Germany - BBC News
maintext: The timing is largely irrelevant. Why now? Well, why not. But if whoever did this hoped to contain the fallout - a mysterious collapse, never explained by Russian doctors - the fact Navalny's team got him to Germany has blown that calculation.
